I'll help you... It was a great
idea...

1:23:58.167 --> 1:24:00.750
I really liked the idea. It was
a great idea.

1:24:01.250 --> 1:24:02.750
I'll make it with you.

1:24:03.667 --> 1:24:05.167
We'll start from the
beginning...

1:24:05.792 --> 1:24:08.125
We'll start over again from the
beginning.

1:24:09.500 --> 1:24:10.875
We'll make a new model and

1:24:10.917 --> 1:24:13.042
I'll put on the little bushes
like you wanted.

1:24:15.693 --> 1:24:17.459
Mama!

1:24:18.042 --> 1:24:20.208
Mom, we'll start again from the
beginning.

1:24:20.750 --> 1:24:22.500
I'm going to help you this time.

1:24:25.469 --> 1:24:27.402
Mama...

1:26:40.804 --> 1:26:43.305
Damn the sun.

1:26:43.307 --> 1:26:44.906
Is it night already then?

1:26:44.908 --> 1:26:46.775
No.

1:26:46.777 --> 1:26:49.845
- Then what is it?
- Gray.

1:26:51.482 --> 1:26:52.714
Gray.

1:26:53.984 --> 1:26:55.884
Gray!

1:26:59.890 --> 1:27:02.424
Gray.

1:27:02.426 --> 1:27:04.393
Gray!

1:27:04.395 --> 1:27:06.328
Did I hear you say gray?

1:27:06.330 --> 1:27:07.729
Light black.

1:27:07.731 --> 1:27:09.431
From pole to pole.

1:27:09.433 --> 1:27:10.866
You exaggerate.

1:27:12.903 --> 1:27:15.370
Don't stay there,
you give me the shivers.

1:27:24.081 --> 1:27:26.648
Why this farce, day after day?

1:27:27.918 --> 1:27:31.053
Routine. One never knows.

1:27:34.425 --> 1:27:37.793
Last night I saw into my breast.

1:27:39.863 --> 1:27:41.830
There was a big sore.

1:27:41.832 --> 1:27:44.399
Pah! You saw your heart.

1:27:45.669 --> 1:27:48.637
No, it was living.

1:27:48.639 --> 1:27:50.706
I wonder.

1:27:53.744 --> 1:27:56.478
If a rational being came
back to earth,

1:27:56.480 --> 1:27:58.980
wouldn't he begin to have
ideas in his head

1:27:58.982 --> 1:28:00.949
if he observed us long enough.

1:28:02.453 --> 1:28:04.052
Ah, yes,

1:28:04.054 --> 1:28:06.588
now I see it.

1:28:06.590 --> 1:28:09.858
Ah... yes, now I understand
what they're at!

1:28:17.501 --> 1:28:19.901
And without going so far
as that,

1:28:21.538 --> 1:28:22.804
we ourselves...

1:28:23.841 --> 1:28:25.807
we ourselves...

1:28:26.844 --> 1:28:29.044
at certain moments.

1:28:30.581 --> 1:28:31.847
To think perhaps...

1:28:32.950 --> 1:28:35.884
this wasn't all for nothing!
